Detailed Description

Auxiliary data store for xAOD::MissingETAssociationMap_v2.

These are the underlying stores for all MissingETAssociation_v2 entries in the composition map.

Note:
The variable names used in this store are the keys in the auxiliary store. To access the data, these keys have to be used with exactly the same spelling as the variable names.
